					<img src="http://archive.org/download/universal_declaration_librivox/Universal_Declaration_of_Human_Rights_1110.jpg" alt="book-cover-large" width="175" height="175" />

										<a href="http://archive.org/download/universal_declaration_librivox/Universal_Declaration_of_Human_Rights_1110.jpg" class="download-cover">Download cover art</a>
					
